Package: BacTools
Title: Automated Software Catalog Creator for Bacterial Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Tasmine", "Clement", , "tasmine@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automates discovery of software tools for bacterial and
    microbiome data analysis by querying CRAN, Bioconductor, and GitHub
    for packages and repositories matching a set of search tags. Results
    are combined into a single de-duplicated catalog with metadata
    (author, DOI, citation, license, release date, and category) and can
    be exported to CSV for downstream use.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
